  "detailed_description": "Argus Panoptes is a 2D platformer with engaging mechanics in an unforgiving world. Find your way through cryptic ruins and debris, in a post apocalyptic universe, where mythology meets a futuristic dystopia of ever-present surveillance.<br><br>Try staying vigilant, cleverly manipulating the invasive, all-watching eyes of Argus, in a dark, obsessive quest for freedom.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/babe18e4700364941dedb49b5c3414f8.poster.avif?t=1631890983\" width=608 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/babe18e4700364941dedb49b5c3414f8.webm?t=1631890983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/babe18e4700364941dedb49b5c3414f8.mp4?t=1631890983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hard-to-master Physics Mechanics</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Spawn forcefields to bounce the eye<br></li><li>Use your \"Force\" ability to alter the trajectory of the eye<br></li><li>Use your \"Slow\" ability to gain more control over the eye<br></li><li>Combine your abilities to precisely navigate the eye through the levels</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Quick tutorial levels to get you up to speed with the mechanics<br></li><li>Compare your time with other players on global leaderboards<br></li><li>Survival (time-attack) mode</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/fb266a9e0e362d4bd9beb46fe045dfb7.poster.avif?t=1631890983\" width=796 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/fb266a9e0e362d4bd9beb46fe045dfb7.webm?t=1631890983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/fb266a9e0e362d4bd9beb46fe045dfb7.mp4?t=1631890983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Argus Panoptes is a 2D platformer with engaging mechanics in an unforgiving world. Find your way through cryptic ruins and debris, in a post apocalyptic universe, where mythology meets a futuristic dystopia of ever-present surveillance.<br><br>Try staying vigilant, cleverly manipulating the invasive, all-watching eyes of Argus, in a dark, obsessive quest for freedom.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/babe18e4700364941dedb49b5c3414f8.poster.avif?t=1631890983\" width=608 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/babe18e4700364941dedb49b5c3414f8.webm?t=1631890983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/babe18e4700364941dedb49b5c3414f8.mp4?t=1631890983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hard-to-master Physics Mechanics</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Spawn forcefields to bounce the eye<br></li><li>Use your \"Force\" ability to alter the trajectory of the eye<br></li><li>Use your \"Slow\" ability to gain more control over the eye<br></li><li>Combine your abilities to precisely navigate the eye through the levels</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Quick tutorial levels to get you up to speed with the mechanics<br></li><li>Compare your time with other players on global leaderboards<br></li><li>Survival (time-attack) mode</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/fb266a9e0e362d4bd9beb46fe045dfb7.poster.avif?t=1631890983\" width=796 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680400/extras/fb266a9e0e362d4bd